<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l24">Den von <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_208_r1l25"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wır tun <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wiſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır vor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l26"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> <expan>vıcʒtum<ex>m</ex></expan> vnd Reten in <expan>nid<ex>er</ex>n</expan> payern . <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag laıſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l27"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ʒu Strawbıng . mıt vveinmar Eker von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprüch <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l28">ʒu vns maynt ʒu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . auf den ſamſtag am achttentag vor ſand </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l29">Bartholmeus tag ſchıerıſt . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l30">Daʒ Jr vns eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auſʒ <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> Rat . auf <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag leıhen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l31">ordiniern wellet . / daʒ dıe mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> . ſo ſıe ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l32"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . fürbas auf den tag vollreıten vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> glimpf vnd vnglimpf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l33">da <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> des wol getrawen . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_208_r1l34"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> larencij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_208" id="104r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Regensp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> wir tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir vor <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan>
<expan>vicztum<ex>m</ex></expan> und reten in <expan>Nid<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        Payern <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag laisten
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> zu Strawbing mit Weinmar Eker von
                                <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sprüch
                            <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die er zu uns maynt zu
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">samstag am achttentag vor sand Bartholmeus tag
                                    schierist</q>17.08.1415</note>
</app>. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, daz ir uns ewr erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ausz
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> rat auf
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag leihen und ordiniern wellet, daz
                        die mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan>, so sie zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, fürbas auf den tag vollreiten und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> glimpf und unglimpf da
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> des wol getrawen. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Larencii. </ab>
</div>
